    <title><![CDATA[Install LNMP on CentOS7]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.lidongwei.com/2015/12/27/Install%20LNMP%20on%20CentOS7/"/>
    <id>http://blog.lidongwei.com/2015/12/27/Install LNMP on CentOS7/</id>
    <published>2015-12-26T17:36:51.925Z</published>
    <updated>2015-12-09T11:58:12.260Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>安装nginx<br><figure class="highlight xquery"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[user@loaclhost ~]$ sudo yum <span class="keyword">update</span></span><br><span class="line">[user@loaclhost ~]$ sudo yum upgrade</span><br><span class="line">[user@loaclhost ~]$ sudo yum install epel-release</span><br><span class="line">[user@loaclhost ~]$ sudo yum install nginx</span><br><span class="line">[user@loaclhost ~]$ sudo systemctl <span class="keyword">start</span> nginx</span><br><span class="line">[user@loaclhost ~]$ sudo systemctl enable nginx.service</span><br><span class="line">[user@loaclhost ~]$ sudo systemctl reload nginx.service</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[user@loaclhost ~]$ sudo vi /etc/nginx/conf.d/user.conf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">server &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    listen       <span class="number">80</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    server_name  domainname.com;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    # note that these lines are originally from the <span class="string">"location /"</span> block</span><br><span class="line">    root   /home/user/www;</span><br><span class="line">    index index.php index.html index.htm;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    location / &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        try_files <span class="variable">$uri</span> <span class="variable">$uri</span>/ =<span class="number">404</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    error_page <span class="number">404</span> /<span class="number">404</span>.html;</span><br><span class="line">    error_page <span class="number">500</span> <span class="number">502</span> <span class="number">503</span> <span class="number">504</span> /<span class="number">50</span>x.html;</span><br><span class="line">    location = /<span class="number">50</span>x.html &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        root /usr/share/nginx/html;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    location ~ \.php$ &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        try_files <span class="variable">$uri</span> =<span class="number">404</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        fastcgi_split_path_info ^(.+\.php)(/.+)$;</span><br><span class="line">        fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php-fpm/php-fpm.sock;</span><br><span class="line">        fastcgi_index index.php;</span><br><span class="line">        fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME <span class="variable">$document</span>_root<span class="variable">$fastcgi</span>_script_name;</span><br><span class="line">        include fastcgi_params;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>安装php<br><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[user@loaclhost ~]$ sudo yum <span class="operator"><span class="keyword">install</span> php php-mysql php-fpm</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="keyword">user</span>@loaclhost ~]$ sudo systemctl <span class="keyword">start</span> php-fpm</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="keyword">user</span>@loaclhost ~]$ sudo systemctl <span class="keyword">enable</span> php-fpm</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="keyword">user</span>@loaclhost ~]$ sudo vi /etc/php-fpm.<span class="keyword">d</span>/www.conf</span><br><span class="line">listen = /<span class="keyword">var</span>/run/php-fpm/php-fpm.sock</span><br><span class="line">listen.owner = nobody</span><br><span class="line">listen.<span class="keyword">group</span> = nobody</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">user</span> = nginx</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">group</span> = nginx</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>新建用户<br><figure class="highlight crystal"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>sudo useradd -g nginx user2</span><br><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>sudo chmod <span class="number">750</span> /home/user2/www -<span class="constant">R</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>安装mysql数据库<br><figure class="highlight crystal"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>sudo yum install mariadb mariadb-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>初始化设置mysql<br><figure class="highlight crystal"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>sudo mysql_secure_installation</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>用root账号登陆mysql<br><figure class="highlight crystal"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>sudo mysql -u root -p</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>创建数据库和用户<br><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title">MariaDB</span> [(<span class="built_in">none</span>)]&gt; CREATE DATABASE database_name;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="title">MariaDB</span> [(<span class="built_in">none</span>)]&gt; CREATE USER <span class="string">'user_name'</span>@<span class="string">'localhost'</span> IDENTIFIED BY <span class="string">'password'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="title">MariaDB</span> [(<span class="built_in">none</span>)]&gt; GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON database_<span class="regexp">name.*</span> TO <span class="string">'user_name'</span>@<span class="string">'localhost'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="title">MariaDB</span> [(<span class="built_in">none</span>)]&gt; FLUSH PRIVILEGES;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>查看所有用户<br><figure class="highlight nsis"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">MariaDB [(<span class="literal">none</span>)]&gt; MariaDB [(<span class="literal">none</span>)]&gt; SELECT <span class="literal">user</span>,host,<span class="literal">user</span> FROM mysql.<span class="literal">user</span><span class="comment">;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>参看所有数据库<br><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title">MariaDB</span> [(<span class="built_in">none</span>)]&gt; SHOW DATABASES;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>参看所有表<br><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title">MariaDB</span> [(<span class="built_in">none</span>)]&gt; USE database_name;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="title">MariaDB</span> [database_name]&gt; SHOW TABLES;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>退出<br><figure class="highlight fortran"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">MariaDB [(<span class="type">none</span>)]&gt; <span class="keyword">exit</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>安装wordpress和自动更新<br><figure class="highlight elixir"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>wget <span class="symbol">http:</span>/<span class="regexp">/wordpress.org/latest</span>.tar.gz;</span><br><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>chown -<span class="constant">R </span><span class="symbol">nginx:</span>nginx wp-content</span><br><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>vi wp-config.php</span><br><span class="line">添加</span><br><span class="line">define(<span class="string">'FS_METHOD'</span>, <span class="string">'direct'</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>其他：<br><figure class="highlight crystal"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>vi /etc/sudoers</span><br><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>sudo yum install vsftpd</span><br><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>sudo systemctl start vsftpd</span><br><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>sudo systemctl enable vsftpd.service</span><br><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>sudo yum install lrzsz</span><br><span class="line">[user<span class="variable">@loaclhost</span> ~]<span class="variable">$ </span>sudo cp /usr/share/zoneinfo/<span class="constant">Asia</span>/<span class="constant">Shanghai</span> /etc/localtime</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
]]></content>
